research-bookmarks-public

This repository contains public-safe bookmark taxonomy and official-source catalog material.

Repository-owned code, scripts, schemas, workflows, and tests are licensed under Apache-2.0.
Repository-owned documentation and taxonomy-style prose may also be used under CC BY 4.0 where explicitly stated.

Private bookmarks, personal notes, browsing history, subjective preference data, account state, and third-party restricted content are excluded from this public catalog and from any public license grant.
